destroyed, so we'll leave from another place

3
00:00:15,156 --> 00:00:16,250
This is the staircase

4
00:00:16,875 --> 00:00:18,151
They brought me from here

5
00:00:18,776 --> 00:00:20,417
They took me into that room

6
00:00:25,729 --> 00:00:30,026
Interviewer: Okay, the ISIS member
came down the stairs and brought you here

7
00:00:30,260 --> 00:00:32,969
When you entered this
place, what could you see?

8
00:00:32,994 --> 00:00:34,609
This room had nobody in it

9
00:00:34,922 --> 00:00:36,823
There were no prisoners in it

10
00:00:37,760 --> 00:00:38,880
In this room

11
00:00:41,506 --> 00:00:44,396
That room has prisoners in it

12
00:00:44,761 --> 00:00:46,740
They put us into that room

13
00:00:47,625 --> 00:00:49,657
The first room
next to the stairs

14
00:00:50,698 --> 00:00:53,016
There were prisoners
with us inside

15
00:00:57,417 --> 00:00:59,136
Interviewer: You
entered through this door

16
00:00:59,188 --> 00:01:03,928
And one of the ISIS members
