17
00:01:03,953 --> 00:01:06,349
When you went in,
what did you see?

18
00:01:06,766 --> 00:01:10,308
What do you remember about
this place when you entered?

19
00:01:10,959 --> 00:01:15,021
When I entered, there was
a guard sitting here at a table

20
00:01:15,776 --> 00:01:18,146
There was a table,
and sitting there

21
00:01:18,615 --> 00:01:19,683
An ISIS member

22
00:01:20,483 --> 00:01:25,066
And there was also an ISIS
member standing in this spot

23
00:01:25,691 --> 00:01:28,035
And this hall was empty

24
00:01:28,712 --> 00:01:30,040
It held no prisoners

25
00:01:31,134 --> 00:01:36,993
Because their surveillance
monitor and cameras were here

26
00:01:37,644 --> 00:01:39,623
A monitor where they watched
what was happening outside

27
00:01:46,186 --> 00:01:50,431
Interviewer: According to your description,
there were no prisoners in this place

28
00:01:50,456 --> 00:01:53,191
There were no prisoners
when they brought me in here

29
00:01:53,216 --> 00:01:55,821
When they took me up the
stairs to here, the hall was empty

30
00:01:56,264 --> 00:01:57,488
There were only ISIS members

31
00:01:58,087 --> 00:02:00,847
And they took us to
that room immediately

32
00:02:01,785 --> 00:02:03,269
That small room

33
00:02:03,834 --> 00:02:06,334
Interviewer: What sounds
did you hear in this place?

34
00:02:06,770 --> 00:02:09,791
There was no one here, but
over there, there were prisoners

35
00:02:10,546 --> 00:02:11,848
That's where they were held

36
00:02:13,203 --> 00:02:18,359
Interviewer: Alright,
take a look at the place

37
00:02:19,817 --> 00:02:22,551
They may have
turned it into a prison

38
00:02:23,098 --> 00:02:28,462
But when they brought me
in from here, it wasn't a prison

39
00:02:29,531 --> 00:02:31,536
Maybe after that, it was
converted into a prison

40
00:02:32,317 --> 00:02:33,723
Meaning it was
turned into a prison

41
00:02:36,614 --> 00:02:43,229
Interviewer: What is different between
when you first entered this place and now?

42
00:02:46,448 --> 00:02:49,261
The place was bombed.
That's what changed

43
00:02:49,772 --> 00:02:53,028
It was a solid room,
and now it's blasted

44
00:02:54,981 --> 00:02:57,220
Interviewer: What
was in this place?

45
00:02:57,245 --> 00:03:03,183
This was where the camera
surveillance monitor was

46
00:03:04,538 --> 00:03:08,835
They had external cameras

47
00:03:11,153 --> 00:03:12,611
They had external cameras

48
00:03:13,444 --> 00:03:19,147
Whoever entered or left their
prison, they watched them on the cameras

49
00:03:21,517 --> 00:03:22,741
And the prisoners too

50
00:03:24,251 --> 00:03:26,491
They had a camera
pointed at the prisoners

51
00:03:29,512 --> 00:03:32,871
Interviewer: Did the ISIS
member take you straight inside?

52
00:03:32,896 --> 00:03:34,564
Yes, he took me
straight into the cell

53
00:03:35,475 --> 00:03:39,668
Interviewer: Is it possible
for you to show us the place?

54
00:03:39,693 --> 00:03:42,975
There was a table here where
an ISIS member used to sit

55
00:03:43,340 --> 00:03:45,267
And another ISIS member here

56
00:03:46,231 --> 00:03:47,481
In this spot

57
00:03:48,210 --> 00:03:49,590
And they put me in here

58
00:03:58,835 --> 00:04:00,866
There were
prisoners in this room

59
00:04:00,891 --> 00:04:02,246
Interviewer: How did you know
there were prisoners inside?

60
00:04:02,271 --> 00:04:04,408
I heard them; they were talking

61
00:04:04,434 --> 00:04:06,491
Interviewer: Could you hear them?
Witness: Yes, I could hear them

62
00:04:06,516 --> 00:04:09,147
Was the door closed?
Witness: Yes, it was closed

63
00:04:09,616 --> 00:04:10,736
Interviewer: And
what is this place?

64
00:04:11,122 --> 00:04:13,362
This used to be a toilet

65
00:04:13,753 --> 00:04:15,654
Interviewer: Did you come here?

66
00:04:15,679 --> 00:04:20,263
They would open the door for you
and let you use the toilet normally

67
00:04:21,148 --> 00:04:23,284
If you asked to go to the
washbasins, he would let you in

68
00:04:24,768 --> 00:04:26,539
And this is the room we were in

69
00:04:27,372 --> 00:04:28,961
They detained me in this room

70
00:04:29,794 --> 00:04:32,997
I spent one day
and left the next day
